      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·齊風·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">著.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>俟我於著乎而，充耳以素乎而，尚之以瓊華乎而。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He was waiting for me between the door and the screen.
The strings of his ear-stoppers were of white silk,
And there were appended to them beautiful Hua-stones.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
