      <prop type="x-translation-ref">著.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>俟我於庭乎而，充耳以青乎而，尚之以瓊瑩乎而。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He was waiting for me in the open court.
The strings of his ear-stoppers were of green silk,
And there were appended to them beautiful Ying-stones.</seg>
      </tuv>
