      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>俟我於堂乎而，充耳以黃乎而，尚之以瓊英乎而。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He was waiting for me in the hall.
